Steven R. Markevich 
Executive Compensation
As Executive Vice President and President, Transportation Coatings & Greater China at AXALTA COATING SYSTEMS LTD, Steven R. Markevich  made $2,626,003 in total compensation.  Of this total $568,269 was received as a salary, $478,688 was received as a bonus, $374,998 was received in stock options, $1,173,362 was awarded as stock and $30,686 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


